Binary files such as `app/src/main/res/mipmap-xhdpi/ic_launcher.png` cannot be represented as text-based code. Please provide a description of the desired launcher icon (e.g., a dog paw with a heart), or use image editing tools like Android Asset Studio or Figma to generate the appropriate PNG assets for each density bucket (mdpi, hdpi, xhdpi, xxhdpi, xxxhdpi). Place the generated images in their respective `mipmap-` directories to ensure proper display across device screen densities.